I quit the FV server long ago, partially over language problems. However, Before I quit I noticed an oddity with my level 12 barbian shaman of about a week or two:<br>
<br>
Yeah, she started with master of human and barb then she ran around in various travels and got one in dwarf, dark elf, gnome, etc. <br>
<br>
The odd thing was that halfling and dark elf then showed up at her trainer but the dwarf and gnome that she got as much as 2 points in while grouping in butcher never did. Consequently by level 12 I had like a bunch of points in each since I could continually train just halfling and dark elf at the trainer.. odd. I never had another language show up at the trainer like that. every time I leveled i ran back to halas to train them some more. <p><center><BR>
